title: liblink: incompatible type signatures for utfrune
body:
On the dev.cc branch, the plan9-386-gcepartial builder is broken with:

```
qtoken: incompatible type signatures 9b47f185(/tmp/buildlet-scatch427100321/go/pkg/obj/plan9_386/lib9.a(utfrune)) and c54741c6(/386/lib/libc.a(tokenize)) for utfrune
go tool dist: FAILED: 8l -o /tmp/buildlet-scatch427100321/go/pkg/tool/plan9_386/8a /tmp/go-tool-dist-168419734/lex.8 /tmp/go-tool-dist-168419734/y.tab.8 /tmp/buildlet-scatch427100321/go/pkg/obj/plan9_386/liblink.a /tmp/buildlet-scatch427100321/go/pkg/obj/plan9_386/libbio.a /tmp/buildlet-scatch427100321/go/pkg/obj/plan9_386/lib9.a
```
